{"title":"前端框架Vue学习第二天","uid":"56e5029f2d3682a6944c532038f68914","slug":"Vue-Day2","date":"2020-04-01T07:56:08.000Z","updated":"2020-05-08T01:42:35.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Vue-Day2.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h2 id=\"Vue过滤器的使用\"><a href=\"#Vue过滤器的使用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Vue过滤器的使用\"></a>Vue过滤器的使用</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>Vue.js 允许你自定义过滤器，可被用于一些常见的文本格式化。过滤器调用时的格式 {{name|过滤器名称}}</p></blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>你可以在一个组件的选项中定义本地的过滤器：<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-html\" data-language=\"html\"><code class=\"language-html\">&lt;body&gt;\n     &lt;div id&#x3D;&quot;app&quot;&gt;&#123;&#123;msg|msgFormat&#125;&#125;&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n     &lt;script&gt;\n         var vm &#x3D; new Vue(&#123;\n             el:&#39;#app&#39;,\n             data:&#123;\n                 msg:&quot;欢迎学习Vue&quot;\n             &#125;,\n             &#x2F;&#x2F;私有过滤器（局部）\n             filters:&#123;\n                msgFormat:function(msg)&#123;\n                    return msg+&quot;------------&quot;\n                &#125;\n             &#125;\n         &#125;) \n     &lt;&#x2F;script&gt;    \n &lt;&#x2F;body&gt;</code></pre></li>\n<li>或者在创建 Vue 实例之前全局定义过滤器：<pre class=\"line-numbers language-html\" data-language=\"html\"><code class=\"language-html\">&lt;body&gt;\n     &lt;div id&#x3D;&quot;app&quot;&gt;&#123;&#123;msg|msgFormat&#125;&#125;&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n     &lt;script&gt;\n         Vue.filter(&#39;msgFormat&#39;,function(msg)&#123;\n             return msg.replace(&quot;Vue&quot;,&quot;Vue框架&quot;)\n         &#125;)\n         var vm &#x3D; new Vue(&#123;\n             el:&#39;#app&#39;,\n             data:&#123;\n                 msg:&quot;欢迎学习Vue&quot;\n             &#125;\n         &#125;)   \n     &lt;&#x2F;script&gt;  \n &lt;&#x2F;body&gt;</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"Vue自定义指令\"><a href=\"#Vue自定义指令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Vue自定义指令\"></a>Vue自定义指令</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>除了核心功能默认内置的指令 (v-model 和 v-show)，Vue 也允许注册自定义指令</p></blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>你可以在一个组件的选项中定义本地的自定义指令：<pre class=\"line-numbers language-html\" data-language=\"html\"><code class=\"language-html\">&lt;body&gt;\n     &lt;div id&#x3D;&quot;app&quot;&gt;\n         &lt;input value&#x3D;&quot;text&quot; v-focus value&#x3D;&quot;hello&quot;&gt;\n     &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n     &lt;script&gt;\n         var vm &#x3D; new Vue(&#123;\n             el:&#39;#app&#39;,\n             data:&#123;\n                 msg:&quot;欢迎学习Vue&quot;\n             &#125;,\n             &#x2F;&#x2F;自定义私有指令\n             directives:&#123;\n                 &#39;focus&#39;:&#123;\n                    inserted:function(el)&#123;\n                         el.focus()\n                     &#125;,\n                 &#125;\n             &#125;\n         &#125;)\n     &lt;&#x2F;script&gt;   \n &lt;&#x2F;body&gt;</code></pre></li>\n<li>或者在创建 Vue 实例之前全局定义自定义指令：<pre class=\"line-numbers language-html\" data-language=\"html\"><code class=\"language-html\">&lt;body&gt;\n     &lt;div id&#x3D;&quot;app&quot;&gt;\n         &lt;input value&#x3D;&quot;text&quot; v-focus value&#x3D;&quot;hello&quot;&gt;\n     &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n     &lt;script&gt;\n         &#x2F;&#x2F;定义全局指令\n         Vue.directive(&#39;focus&#39;,&#123;\n             bind:function(el)&#123;\n                \n             &#125;,\n             inserted:function(el)&#123;\n                 el.focus()\n             &#125;,\n             updated:function(el)&#123;\n\n             &#125;\n         &#125;)\n         var vm &#x3D; new Vue(&#123;\n             el:&#39;#app&#39;,\n             data:&#123;\n                 msg:&quot;欢迎学习Vue&quot;\n             &#125;\n         &#125;)\n     &lt;&#x2F;script&gt;   \n &lt;&#x2F;body&gt;\n</code></pre>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>一个指令定义对象可以提供如下几个钩子函数 (均为可选)：<br>bind：只调用一次，指令第一次绑定到元素时调用。在这里可以进行一次性的初始化设置。<br>inserted：被绑定元素插入父节点时调用 (仅保证父节点存在，但不一定已被插入文档中)。<br>update：所在组件的 VNode 更新时调用，但是可能发生在其子 VNode 更新之前。指令的值可能发生了改变，也可能没有。但是你可以通过比较更新前后的值来忽略不必要的模板更新 (详细的钩子函数参数见<a href=\"https://vuejs.bootcss.com/guide/custom-directive.html\">Vue官方文档</a>）。</p></blockquote>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"Vue生命周期函数\"><a href=\"#Vue生命周期函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Vue生命周期函数\"></a>Vue生命周期函数</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-html\" data-language=\"html\"><code class=\"language-html\">&lt;body&gt;\n    &lt;div id&#x3D;&quot;app&quot;&gt;&#123;&#123;msg&#125;&#125;&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n    &lt;script&gt;\n        var vm &#x3D; new Vue(&#123;\n            el:&#39;#app&#39;,\n            data:&#123;\n                msg:&quot;欢迎学习Vue&quot;\n            &#125;,\n            beforeCreate()&#123;\n               alert(this.msg)\n            &#125;,\n            created()&#123;\n                alert(this.msg)\n            &#125;,\n            beforeMount()&#123;\n                 \n            &#125;,\n            mounted()&#123;\n\n            &#125;,\n            beforeUpdate()&#123;\n\n            &#125;,\n            updated()&#123;\n\n            &#125;,\n            beforeDestroy()&#123;\n\n            &#125;,\n            destroyed()&#123;\n                \n            &#125;\n\n        &#125;)\n    &lt;&#x2F;script&gt;\n    \n&lt;&#x2F;body&gt;</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>生命周期图示<div align=center>\n <img width=600 src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200408182654.png\" >\n</div></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"vue-resource发起get-post-jsonp请求\"><a href=\"#vue-resource发起get-post-jsonp请求\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"vue-resource发起get,post,jsonp请求\"></a>vue-resource发起get,post,jsonp请求</h2><ul>\n<li>添加<code>&lt;script src=&quot;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/vue-resource@1.5.1&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</code><br>引入vue-resource<pre class=\"line-numbers language-html\" data-language=\"html\"><code class=\"language-html\">&lt;body&gt;\n    &lt;div id&#x3D;&quot;app&quot;&gt;\n        &lt;input value&#x3D;&quot;get&quot; type&#x3D;&quot;button&quot; @click&#x3D;&quot;getInfo&quot;&gt;\n    &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n    &lt;script&gt;\n        var vm &#x3D; new Vue(&#123;\n            el:&#39;#app&#39;,\n            data:&#123;\n                msg:&quot;欢迎学习Vue&quot;\n            &#125;,\n            methods:&#123;\n                getInfo()&#123;\n                    this.$http.get(&#39;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;vue.studyit.io&#x2F;api&#x2F;getlunbo&#39;).then(function(result)&#123;\n                        console.log(result)\n                    &#125;)\n                &#125;\n            &#125;\n        &#125;)\n    &lt;&#x2F;script&gt;\n    \n&lt;&#x2F;body&gt;</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n","text":"Vue过滤器的使用 Vue.js 允许你自定义过滤器，可被用于一些常见的文本格式化。过滤器调用时的格式 {{name|过滤器名称}} 你可以在一个组件的选项中定义本地的过滤器： &lt;body&gt; &lt;div id&#x3D;&quot;app&quot;&gt;&#1...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"4.7k","symbolsTime":"4 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Vue","slug":"Vue","count":12,"path":"api/categories/Vue.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"前端","slug":"前端","count":13,"path":"api/tags/前端.json"},{"name":"Vue","slug":"Vue","count":12,"path":"api/tags/Vue.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Vue%E8%BF%87%E6%BB%A4%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Vue过滤器的使用</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Vue%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Vue自定义指令</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Vue%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%9F%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Vue生命周期函数</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#vue-resource%E5%8F%91%E8%B5%B7get-post-jsonp%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82\"><span class=\"toc-text\">vue-resource发起get,post,jsonp请求</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"CHEN","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109161140460.jpg","link":"/","description":"学无止境","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/cjpnice","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"Android开发：Fragment的使用方法","uid":"131971b6f04109d06f5f9a9629112392","slug":"Android-Fragment","date":"2020-04-01T14:38:24.000Z","updated":"2020-05-08T01:40:17.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Android-Fragment.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"text":"什么是Fragment Fragment是一个可以将activity拆分成几个完全独立封装的可重用的组件，每个组件有自己的生命周期和ui布局。 Fragment的生命周期 Fragment的简单用法 创建左边的Fragment布局文件,布局中添加一个按钮&lt;?xml vers...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"7.3k","symbolsTime":"7 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Android","slug":"Android","count":16,"path":"api/categories/Android.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","count":25,"path":"api/tags/Java.json"},{"name":"Android","slug":"Android","count":16,"path":"api/tags/Android.json"}],"author":{"name":"CHEN","slug":"blog-author"